HEADWORD: Atacamite
<hw>A*tac"a*mite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From the
desert of <etsep>Atacama</etsep>, where found.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
